data.description: ***$5,000 SELLER CREDIT TO BUYER!*** *ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 4.2% RATE* Nestled in the heart of Homestead, this brand-new 2022 townhouse offers a perfect fusion of modern elegance and everyday comfort. With three spacious bedrooms, 2.5 luxurious bathrooms, and two well-designed floors, this home provides ample space for you and your loved ones. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the contemporary design and high-end finishes that make this property truly special. Whether you're looking to relax in the generously sized living spaces, cook up a storm in the stylish kitchen, or unwind in the private outdoor area, this townhouse has it all. It's an incredible opportunity to experience the best of new construction in a thriving community.
